<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Inertia_characteristics_mim  Entity: moments_of_inertia_representation  
   <express_ref linkend="inertia_characteristics:mim:Inertia_characteristics_mim.moments_of_inertia_representation"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Inertia_characteristics_mim.moments_of_inertia_representation">
A <b>moments_of_inertia_representation</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> that describes the law of inertia of a rigid body. 
<p>The 9 inertia values are represented as a <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.list_representation_item"/> containing 3 elements, each describing one row of the inertia matrix, and each having 3 elements that describe the columns of each row. 
</p>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Inertia_characteristics_mim  Entity: moments_of_inertia_representation  Where: WR1 
   <express_ref linkend="furniture_catalog_and_interior_design_cc1:mim:Inertia_characteristics_mim.moments_of_inertia_representation.wr:WR1"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Inertia_characteristics_mim.moments_of_inertia_representation.wr:WR1">
The <b>moments_of_inertia_representation</b> shall contain exactly one <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> item in its set of items. 
<p>This <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> item shall be of type <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.compound_representation_item"/> and have a name of 'moments of inertia matrix'. 
</p></ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Inertia_characteristics_mim  Entity: moments_of_inertia_representation  Where: WR2 
   <express_ref linkend="furniture_catalog_and_interior_design_cc1:mim:Inertia_characteristics_mim.moments_of_inertia_representation.wr:WR2"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Inertia_characteristics_mim.moments_of_inertia_representation.wr:WR2">
The <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.compound_representation_item"/> that is contained in the <b>moments_of_inertia_representation</b> shall reference exactly three <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> items. 
<p>These <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> items shall be of type <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.compound_representation_item"/> and reached through <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.list_representation_item"/>. 
</p>
<p>Each of these <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.compound_representation_item"/> references three measure representation items through <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.list_representation_item"/>. 
</p>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Inertia_characteristics_mim  Rule: restrict_centre_of_mass_representation 
   <express_ref linkend="inertia_characteristics:mim:Inertia_characteristics_mim.restrict_centre_of_mass_representation"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Inertia_characteristics_mim.restrict_centre_of_mass_representation">
The <b>restrict_centre_of_mass_representation</b> rule specifies that each instance of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> with a name of 'centre of mass' shall contain exactly one item in its set of items. 
This <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.compound_representation_item"/> shall be of type point and shall have a name of 'centre point'. 
<p>This rule enforces the requirement for every <b>Centre_of_mass</b> to have exactly one centre point. 
</p>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Inertia_characteristics_mim  Entity: restrict_centre_of_mass_representation  Where: WR1 
   <express_ref linkend="furniture_catalog_and_interior_design_cc1:mim:Inertia_characteristics_mim.restrict_centre_of_mass_representation.wr:WR1"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Inertia_characteristics_mim.restrict_centre_of_mass_representation.wr:WR1">
Each instance of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/> with a name of 'centre of mass' shall contain exactly one item in its set of items. 
This <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.compound_representation_item"/> shall be of type point and shall have a name of 'centre point'.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Inertia_characteristics_mim  Function: value_range_aggregate_rep_item 
   <express_ref linkend="furniture_catalog_and_interior_design_cc1:mim:Inertia_characteristics_mim.value_range_aggregate_rep_item"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Inertia_characteristics_mim.value_range_aggregate_rep_item">
The <b>value_range_aggregate_rep_item</b> function accepts an AGGREGATE of type <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_item"/> as input and returns a boolean result. The function will return TRUE if the elements of the AGGREGATE repesent a 3x3 matrix of <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.measure_representation_item"/> instances. Else it will return FALSE. 
<p>This function is used in the second local rule of <b>moments_of_inertia_representation</b>. 
</p>
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Inertia_characteristics_mim.value_range_aggregate_rep_item.agg">
the aggregate of instances of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.compound_representation_item"/> that is evaluated.
</ext_description>
